comment_data.body: Maybe you didn't restart after upgrading the Flutter plugin? The method `w()` on the first line of your stack trace was removed in v60. I suggest uninstalling the Flutter plugin, installing again from the JetBrains Marketplace, then restarting Android Studio.

Hi!  stevemessick.
Thank you for your reply.

Reinstalling Android Studio is no longer a problem.
